<subSubSection pageId="45" pageNumber="529" type="conservation">
<paragraph blockId="45.[127,1337,1422,2323]" pageId="45" pageNumber="529">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[129,480,2133,2166]" pageId="45" pageNumber="529">Status and Conservation.</emphasis>
Classified as Data Deficient on The IUCN Red List. The Chocoan Nectar Bat is known from less than ten specimens collected in very threatened habitats of the 
<collectingRegion box="[340,431,2211,2244]" country="Panama" name="Embera-Wounaan" pageId="45" pageNumber="529">Choco</collectingRegion>
ecoregion, suggesting it faces conservation threats.
</paragraph>
